{"tid":327250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解明知我好 都唔肯考慮下我","createTime":"2017-07-18T15:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T06:54:34.000Z","uid":72925,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c19e4579bc14c8bdf3e96fb280712d4c6c10fb8","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"點解明知道個ex係衰都要掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解你講就算仲鐘意佢 都唔會再同佢一齊<br />\n但又俾佢聯絡返你 <br />\n明知我好 叫你考慮下我<br />\n次次都覆句 睇下遲下點 哈哈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你就笑得出 我真係笑唔出<br />\n你再係咁 我真係頭也不回 走人<br />\n消失一陣 你再唔主動搵我就算<br />\n我唔想次次都係我搵係你<br />\n不過我消失你都唔會覺得我消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62056319a9168a8d9fe5467f92815a5b03d6b442","tid":327250,"uid":118818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"抽身啦"},{"pid":"effe4fc26d52bb9ec173acc918dd897caee402c9","tid":327250,"uid":66436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"因為你同佢ex既差距大到即使佢咁衰都唔會考慮你"},{"pid":"4f95fc7ed503f5f18af427a86cda1ad57ebbd6c7","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你同佢ex既差距大到即使佢咁衰都唔會考慮你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係佢個ex太差<br />\n可能對佢太好 佢話個感覺好唔真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa3a28419e961195ca15a21f403c4713dd284df","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽身啦</blockquote><br />\n唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e558d6136d54a50c57f0033f81ee1c8f14fcdf","tid":327250,"uid":828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:31:50.000Z","msg":"人地講下咋 咁都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee346046e1c24fcee8656c38c8efa