只係貪心想享齊人之福<br />\n唔好阻住自己去搵幸福啊"},{"pid":"d43a538ad60a652d6c52e24e7111c9b9a81598c2","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢就算搵返你都只係貪心想享齊人之福<br />\n唔好阻住自己去搵幸福啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢係咁既人 應該已經即刻同我一齊<br />\n所以我覺得佢一定唔係咁既人<br />\n我諗佢係當我朋友 份人真心<br />\n所以先同我講自己仲掛住ex <br />\n不過我都係覺得唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我覺得無理由要掛住個ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c25d50c1f394a6e258514679a719199a3ec008d","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算喇，咪阻住人阻住自己喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢同我一齊先會幸福 佢個ex先係阻止嗰個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b0b44fe455110c6d5fbdd1e29e1c618eaca974","tid":327250,"uid":105499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:03:14.000Z","msg":"走啦 唔好哂青春"},{"pid":"5331abe0a78a9d16c5815076d3dbe7432a0d0c34","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身同感受<br />\n睇到喊左出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cbf2e12b049c9b02dcd09c37b56008e1b319d8","tid":327250,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"又一個太年輕既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf1e0d7273d5e7eb93e4aa32be09ba7006427ca","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地講下咋 咁都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都係講下咋 我消失一陣 佢一定會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔准咁講住 俾個希望我 <br />\n我信佢會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db200f6054ff6bcb593f328b9f95e8ff819e2be","tid":327250,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"呢種犯賤動物快d抽身算<br />\n你再等就真係同佢一樣係犯賤啦"},{"pid":"6dbe9f7be27af5ead01263d9e5e464814d8a3f9f","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>走啦 唔好哂青春</blockquote><br />\n如果我今日就走左去 哂青春嗰個就係佢<br />\n其實我都唔想走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b88d21a9e64a6b99057432553cc5005af41971","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又一個太年輕既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一眼就睇出我年輕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5d6c787804a1cc6b03d2d39f6f6f8ccfdfa3a2","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢種犯賤動物快d抽身算<br />\n你再等就真係同佢一樣係犯賤啦</blockquote><br />\n其實我起度諗佢係咪真係有日可以忘記到佢個ex<br />\n其實我想同佢走出陰影 同佢一齊<br />\n依加係擔心佢會一時諗錯 回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51987dd70530c4262e1b3e4d320449a5306f5d9","tid":327250,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"好人卡..."},{"pid":"2370a96d5a5ee0f52912368b0eb339965ea9159d","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"點解無人叫我俾啲時間 等下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人同我一樣等緊一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c989354b531593546ef4a75ecd3084131a148d0d","tid":327250,"uid":31465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"算吧啦"},{"pid":"17a56c95ec11c66b9be7423646eefdc70cddf9c7","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好人卡...</blockquote><br />\n我係好人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢一定唔係派卡俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35a6f6e2a2b8e455316d8db5845ef7e6de6ffcc","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算吧啦</blockquote><br />\n唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d71b6a35bc9e91195e01ba79632e14e233a25a3","tid":327250,"uid":84798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"唔好咁傻喇<br />\n人地有事先搵你渣"},{"pid":"60e00746749abdfcf6d1e29323ed0767a87dae6d","tid":327250,"uid":35063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"等你老母咩 <br />\n係冧你既唔會叫你等啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"fc0ff9727156323e33634a28638c3250699ab57f","tid":327250,"uid":5684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"唔好咁撚低賤啦"},{"pid":"185933d723546dd9023fa5c68c7cbf2b2c314954","tid":327250,"uid":84798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁撚低賤啦</blockquote><br />\n我真係好低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff127a1754546989ea02d31162f74a014af4dc5","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁傻喇<br />\n人地有事先搵你渣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk