rmal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抽身啦</blockquote><br />\n未有feel 可以繼上做朋友先<br />\n好多愛情最初都係由做朋友開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2674d1a428be06292211d19933158078643a71dc","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘意就鐘意<br />\n唔鐘意就唔鐘意<br />\n邊有得遲d睇下點<br />\n可能收兵咋</blockquote><br />\n開頭識佢 係佢驚我收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢邊會收我兵 依加我地係堅過石堅既朋友<br />\n係好既開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86858a8e9d107c2d71ea6db864d67752747b92d6","tid":327250,"uid":72925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你樣衰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話佢ex唔靚 唔知點解鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢無話過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559343782134509fafa213aeae282013cfad0c71","tid":327250,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為你同佢ex既差距大到即使佢咁衰都唔會考慮你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係佢個ex太差<br />\n可能對佢太好 佢話個感覺好唔真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又會咁易哄"},{"pid":"381aeb043d448bb580afa98dbfb53b58f887621c","tid":327250,"uid":178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地講下咋 咁都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都係講下咋 我消失一陣 佢一定會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔准咁講住 俾個希望我 <br />\n我信佢會搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61f4ea8c511f3bedec68af14c87a84416b3de5c"